title: Tobu Bhalobashi
subTitle: While driving on a rainy day, Raj accidently kills a person. Following the incident, Raj visits the victim's family to inform about his sad demise, but ends up falling in love with his pregnant wife.

title: Paapi
subTitle: When Harekrishna offers him a large sum of money, Shambu, a criminal, murders Susanta. Subsequently, his sister Chandra commits suicide due to her love for Susanta.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: To propose marriage on behalf of Lord Shiva, the gods pay a visit to Parvati's parents. However, Mainadevi, Parvati's mother, declines the proposal.

title: Jamai No 1
subTitle: A businessman weds his two eldest daughters to men who now depend on him. However, things take a turn when his third daughter marries a thief.

title: Prem Shakti
subTitle: Ganga and Gauri anger an evil tantric by saving Nagaraj. Enraged, the tantric turns Gauri into stone and kills Ganga. Nagaraj blesses Ganga with rebirth and helps unite him with his love.

title: Champion
subTitle: Jones, a talented and disciplined footballer, is judged by his peers for his financial status. However, when he finds out about his past, he faces a dilemma.

title: Premer Kahini
subTitle: Akash falls in love with Barsha but loses contact with her due to unforeseeable circumstances. While attending a marriage ceremony, he is shocked to realise that the bride is none other than Barsha.

title: Baro Bou
subTitle: Tapan and his wife generously provide for their joint family. However, when the younger brother marries his employer's daughter, he becomes arrogant, which creates a rift within the family.

title: I Love You
subTitle: Santosh, a carefree youth, parts ways with his lover, Dharmika, during his college days. Years later, after his marriage to Gowri, he runs into her, which leaves him in a dilemma.

title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Challenge 2

title: Prohor
subTitle: Nandita, a nurse, one day encounters a case of bomb blast. The patient was none other than a criminal, who raped her six years ago.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: When Mainadevi rejects Lord Shiva's marriage proposal, Parvati is left astounded, and Diti and Tarakasura are delighted by Mainadevi's decision.

title: Bhakter Maa
subTitle: A young woman, who is a devotee of Goddess Bhabatarini, saves a wealthy man from a fatal accident. They soon get married but she turns to the goddess when she faces problems in her marital life.

title: Mukhyamantri
subTitle: Bimal, a school teacher, is distraught when his family asks him to stand up in the upcoming elections for the position of chief minister. However, his opponent, Bibhash, plots against him.

title: Gharer Laxmi
subTitle: Poor bride faces wealthy father-in-law's wrath after he cruelly tries to separate his son from his wife and child, but fate intervenes.

title: Subho Drishti
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Sabuj Saathi
subTitle: Sabuj learns that Sathi, the girl he loves, is his friend Rahul's girlfriend and decides to conceal his feelings for her while secretly doing everything to keep her happy.

title: Bidroho
subTitle: Uttam's ailing mother dies after not getting proper treatment when the landlord refuses to help them. Later, he decides to exact revenge against the injustice done to him.

title: Villain
subTitle: Riya meets Sneha on a flight back home and they strike up a conversation. Surprisingly, Sneha's fiance turns out to be a lookalike of Riya's boyfriend, leaving her in a state of shock.

title: Villain

title: Durga Sohay
subTitle: A mother-daughter relationship develops between Manasi, the younger daughter-in-law of an aristocratic family, and Durga, a maid, when she gives her a second chance after the house-help is caught stealing.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati decides to sacrifice her love against her will to make her parents feel content. Lord Shiva goes on a disguise in order to meet Parvati.

title: Rann
subTitle: Vijay Malik runs his struggling television channel with integrity despite stiff competition. However, his son Jai concocts a plan to take over the business via a fake news story.

title: Prem Pujari
subTitle: Lt Ramdev Bakshi is sent to prison after disobeying the orders given by his seniors. However, he later seeks forgiveness and accepts to work as a spy for the army.

title: Mastan
subTitle: Raju, an orphan, is raised by a smuggler and grows up to become his right-hand man. He decides to quit the life of crime after falling in love but is forced to return when she marries a CBI officer.

title: Bondhoo
subTitle: A devoted father stands up to obstacles and fights against all odds to win legal custody of his young son.

title: Jamai Raja
subTitle: Realising that marriage is her only path to inheriting her father's fortune, a woman gets married to a poor man who is in desperate need of money.

title: Josh
subTitle: Indra, a care-free college student, tries to save his best friend's sister, Anuradha, from a dangerous family dispute, but his efforts lead to unexpected and worsening complications.

title: Babu Shona
subTitle: After a kidnapping in London goes wrong due to an engagement between a kidnapper and a devious thief, their relationship leads to unforeseen consequences.
